---
title: Beef Burger with Baconnaise & Spiced Chips for Dinner with Sichuan-Glazed Beef Patty Rice Bowl for Lunch
description: Cook once, with a twist for lunch. Cook an amazing dinner as usual, then put a new spin on the recipe to create something different for lunch the next day. Dig into a beef burger with baconnaise (our new lovechild!) and spiced chips for dinner, then serve up Asian flavours with beef patties, rice and veggies for lunch. Extra delicious!

